{"tid":55214,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人愈大，愈來愈無朋友","createTime":"2016-12-26T08:30:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T18:00:57.000Z","uid":4303,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3a00bc700ce515b7e6951ef63d51949f4388177e","tid":55214,"uid":4303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:30:01.000Z","msg":"發覺慢慢大，同身邊嘅朋友愈來愈疏遠，唔知係唔係因為價值觀唔同，道原同不相為謀。以前出去玩都好熱鬧，成班人好開心，而家反而唔知搵邊個好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好似覺得成個世界都無人鐘意我，無人在乎我。<br />\n除左屋企人之外，無咩值得留戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"798f03cd9bdbddfc9fb0ab6f5ce1b25d395d69b3","tid":55214,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T09:58:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c62a57f44f0a193644bbf2abcb93521bcc451e8d","tid":55214,"uid":67876,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:11:07.000Z","msg":"約出街食飯 一定唔齊人<br />\n食飯大家愈來愈似普通識既<br />\n當初個種兄弟既感覺<br />\n愈來愈愈消失<br />\n陌生到有時都唔知食飯聚會為咩<br />\n當年既一班兄弟。真係得番個腦裹回憶"},{"pid":"dd874578b3e5e1de8a16fdfe9a43a9a04337511c","tid":55214,"uid":37746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:13:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"72dbb6804dc255fb91a42c1a1546782d79774fa8","tid":55214,"uid":54387,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:29:33.000Z","msg":"人到咁上下年紀<br />\n如果結唔到婚，無兒無女<br />\n九成都會孤零零一個"},{"pid":"2ded64e4160556f1c05f3f2ca87f399bca5b05bb","tid":55214,"uid":30044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:31:24.000Z","msg":"從來沒有 從來都沒有"},{"pid":"a20477b783afe274f686c1b71d1dcb6f3122251a","tid":55214,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:32:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa3019f8d64acbd67a14a67648aeb9d9d28bd305","tid":55214,"uid":54387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:34:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>人到咁上下年紀<br />\n如果結唔到婚，無兒無女<br />\n九成都會孤零零一個</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未必，而家唔少人好遲都未拍拖</blockquote><br />\n嗰班未拍拖嘅<br />\n偏偏佢哋身邊朋友大部份都結晒婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"924dc8fe4bdf863fd62f200cf51119d9f24caec5","tid":55214,"uid":52955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:38:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>發覺慢慢大，同身邊嘅朋友愈來愈疏遠，唔知係唔係因為價值觀唔同，道原同不相為謀。以前出去玩都好熱鬧，成班人好開心，而家反而唔知搵邊個好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好似覺得成個世界都無人鐘意我，無人在乎我。<br />\n除左屋企人之外，無咩值得留戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同路人"},{"pid":"8bb4bc46551257fbd22e99c8860ccf8e69107a3e","tid":55214,"uid":4303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:39:04.000Z","msg":"做緊野啦，而家26<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69faecf4df74e80bf08c06d91734fea02ce81153","tid":55214,"uid":4303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:41:01.000Z","msg":"唯有安慰自己，其實自己一個有咩所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c437c4d3c04ef141d6c6c0bbc06b12298b625170","tid":55214,"uid":4303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:43:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>人到咁上下年紀<br />\n如果結唔到婚，無兒無女<br />\n九成都會孤零零一個</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未必，而家唔少人好遲都未拍拖</blockquote><br />\n嗰班未拍拖嘅<br />\n偏偏佢哋身邊朋友大部份都結晒婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n望返以前熟過嘅朋友開始結婚生仔就覺得我都係孤零零"},{"pid":"2245354c94c992932d90009b52d3db3cf032e369","tid":55214,"uid":51681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:45:22.000Z","msg":"人大左。時間少左。 日日都過得好快。 要識抓緊同朋友相處時間<br />\n要識珍惜同朋友相處時間。"},{"pid":"1f93ecca82238c1a31d48520d0d2fa8859502110","tid":55214,"uid":28960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:46:16.000Z","msg":"有朋友<br />\n但想約一個出黎 訴下苦傾下心事<br />\n真係一個都搵唔到出黎"},{"pid":"5f50a3dd93d370112891ddc4d63fad6208f67d5f","tid":55214,"uid":18547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:46:20.000Z","msg":"朋友愈來愈少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f430047ca167c12350163ff13e96fa932b8487ec","tid":55214,"uid":755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:46:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>發覺慢慢大，同身邊嘅朋友愈來愈疏遠，唔知係唔係因為價值觀唔同，道原同不相為謀。以前出去玩都好熱鬧，成班人好開心，而家反而唔知搵邊個好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好似覺得成個世界都無人鐘意我，無人在乎我。<br />\n除左屋企人之外，無咩值得留戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同意"},{"pid":"fcd0c56dea770a9d66ea7bf1b8d6d027c4edd53f","tid":55214,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:48:36.000Z","msg":"廿歲已經係<br />\n<br />\n約都冇約"},{"pid":"f9dbf37b1818ad46a7e035419617d41c57558a53","tid":55214,"uid":4303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:49:03.000Z","msg":"其實有幾個都仲好熟好friend，但係約親佢地唔得閒，久而久之就覺得算啦，無癮再約，唔想又比人拒絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c74fc28820f49936c70e34e4e6ff385192c6d8cd","tid":55214,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:50:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實有幾個都仲好熟好friend，但係約親佢地唔得閒，久而久之就覺得算啦，無癮再約，唔想又比人拒絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都唔知邊個係friend<br />\n佢地已經有自己圈子"},{"pid":"e7d2442a1d493113f1a5a5e23cdfafc92b568cbf","tid":55214,"uid":755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:51:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未必，而家唔少人好遲都未拍拖</blockquote><br />\n嗰班未拍拖嘅<br />\n偏偏佢哋身邊朋友大部份都結晒婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n望返以前熟過嘅朋友開始結婚生仔就覺得我都係孤零零</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有女既陪女 <br />\n得返自己鳩下鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我成日都自己出街睇下有咩做"},{"pid":"5cfb4ffa5e0d5e489c949f7a60a3c1fad612f6a0","tid":55214,"uid":6869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:51:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0c39ea6daf018be564445e2a4ab00b484653f4a","tid":55214,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:52:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得上少d高登，會樂觀好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會悲觀<br />\n<br />\n至少連登有人同你講嘢"},{"pid":"4212302f9b536302648299a9ff00055c0a6ded91","tid":55214,"uid":56210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:52:40.000Z","msg":"人大了朋友少咗! 可能係大家都各有各忙，但日子久了仍留在身邊的才是真正朋友。交朋應該係重質不重量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87d5280a66c1a2220c78df79d402f51079d21c10","tid":55214,"uid":51681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:54:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人大了朋友少咗! 可能係大家都各有各忙，但日子久了仍留在身邊的才是真正朋友。交朋應該係重質不重量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n重要改變自己心態。人越悲想既野越悲"},{"pid":"2bec62c38df79892c4476412ad90280e30dadd7e","tid":55214,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T11:00:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}